**************


                     Remove_Player

Syntax:    remove_player [name]

Desc:
           removes entries from 'players','mail', and 'board_records' tables
           for player 'name'.
           Also attempts to remove that players .o file, though this may throw
           an error and have to be done manually.

Warning:   Entries in the database can only be restored to a previous state by
           talking to Mizan. Make sure you want to remove!

Example:   remove_player mokri
                  results
           as far as the database is concerned, 'mokri' no longer exists.

